Indeed, in http://wikirank.di.unimi.it/, it is shown that the United States are the center according to harmonic centrality, and many other mea- sures (however, in that work, the ranking is only approximated).

A further evidence for this conjecture comes from the Six Degree of Wikipedia game (http://thewikigame.com/ 6-degrees-of-wikipedia), where a player is asked to go from one page to the other following the smallest possible number of link: a hard variant of this game forces the player not to pass theUnited States page, which is considered to be central.
